{"tid":1603570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"武磊數據：0射門0過人0攔截4傳球 評分排全隊第三(倒數)","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:31:59.000Z","uid":173952,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"63aead64ed3653a15c3a81d47f6c8a49c39b335a","tid":1603570,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"在愛斯賓奴0-2不敵華拉度列的比賽中，武磊後備出場，在球隊10打11的不利局面下，武磊表現機會寥寥。賽後，《whoscored》給他打出全隊倒數第三的5.8分，而在《sofascore》的評分中，武磊得到球隊倒數第五的6.4分。<br />\n<br />\n  據《whoscored》統計，今場武磊共觸球9次（全場最低），完成4次傳球（全場最低），解圍1次，封堵射門1次，其餘射門、過人、攔截等數據均為0。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  在《whoscored》評分中，武磊獲得愛斯賓奴第三低的5.8分，僅高於染紅離場的卡萊羅和正選的山齊士；而在《sofascore》評分中，武磊的得分為6.4分，高於染紅離場的卡萊羅、正選的山齊士、巴爾加斯和後備出場的大衛-盧比斯。"},{"pid":"6fb5508f3f122e0c8fd4e553409117029dc0ad56","tid":1603570,"uid":199081,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"6.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f18bd18a88e247b431ba7ef1d2b883bdb3e3e2","tid":1603570,"uid":36894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"見底了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f573b80cb46c61842b431d1fc40cb6b07c1bb62","tid":1603570,"uid":201158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"隊波排18<br />\n美欺都救唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac88e49c642e3053636e91ad7b1c5b8bfcd0f998","tid":1603570,"uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fb5508f3f122e0c8fd4e553409117029dc0ad56","tid":1603570,"uid":199081,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"6.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkg